in-gewirtz-grossman-llc-announces-investigation-of-apple-inc-appl-2018-02-06", "headline": "SHAREHOLDER ALERT: Bronstein, Gewirtz & Grossman, LLC Announces Investigation of Apple, Inc. (APPL) - MarketWatch"}
